                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素伤害</span>，目标角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">石化</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/c701cbbd15b971aaee458b19e71b4ced_3264352437354071292.png",
